25|$|In 2012, the {{institute}} {{took over the}} responsibility for running the Missilethreat.com website from the Claremont Institute. Missilethreat.com aims to inform the American people of missile threats, thereby encouraging the deployment of a <b>ballistic</b> <b>missile</b> <b>defense</b> system. Since the closure of {{the institute}}, the Missilethreat.com website has been maintained by the Center for Strategic and International Studies.|$|E
